{"tid":760171,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[COVER] 漸漸   N年無玩枝咪都鋪晒塵 細力少少","createTime":"2018-07-29T09:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T01:43:55.000Z","uid":9541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"890db7480b55acf708d1f6c1c6b0b0471787b805","tid":760171,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/ericariel/cover-10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fericariel%2Fcover-10&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=72bb90af\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/ericariel/cover-10</a><br />\n<br />\n今日先裝番ADOBE<br />\nD EFFECT已經唔記得晒點整..<br />\n<br />\n在夜晚 說早晨<br />\n閒談後 你更像別人<br />\n字幕裡 說冬日灰暗<br />\n回答你 這邊的氣氛<br />\n就像你 已記不起了<br />\n連懷舊 也格外寂寥<br />\n雜物裡 遺物和舊照<br />\n誰變賣 誰棄掉 誰看到破曉<br />\n<br />\n漸漸我甚麼都不想知道<br />\n我覺得迷失竟比醒覺好<br />\n漸漸我離開都不想宣佈<br />\n怕記憶 最後變話題 太俗套<br />\n<br />\n別讓我 再失眠<br />\n沉迷後 有美夢未圓<br />\n現實裡 你飄蕩很遠<br />\n還勸我 不應該眷戀<br />\n但是我 卻看得穿了<br />\n誰承諾 似信念動搖<br />\n背誦了 閒話和玩笑<br />\n忘記吧 誰記住 誰要我發表<br />\n<br />\n漸漸我甚麼都不想知道<br />\n我覺得迷失竟比醒覺好<br />\n漸漸我離開都不想宣佈<br />\n怕記憶 最後變話題 太俗套<br />\n<br />\n寂寞 寂寞出於你的空白<br />\n<br />\n剩下我被記憶掌摑<br />\n如留下語錄誰來看<br />\n懷念只可鋪滿被單<br />\n<br />\n漸漸我聞歌都不想起舞<br />\n我覺得我失去一切知覺極美好<br />\n渾噩哪及記得恐怖<br />\n記得種種感覺 但欠你的廝守到老"},{"pid":"0e8e513eec04345cee1936710eeb463ecfa5e79e","tid":760171,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bb16468238fb6c38902fdcd3ff2579873f7cb3","tid":760171,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj